# Memory workflow

- Before non-trivial tasks, read `docs/ai/active.md` and `AGENTS.md`.
- After meaningful work, update `docs/ai/active.md` and `docs/ai/progress.md` (and `decisions.md` / `lessons.md` when relevant).
- Keep memory files short and factual.
- Before committing memory changes, show the user the diff (recommended default).
- Do not invent product requirements that are not in `docs/ai/` or the user’s message.
